        {
          "ability": {
            "ability_type": "offensive",
            "name": "Calculated Reload",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "When the sharpshooter reloads their crossbow, they also calculate the best angle to their target, increasing the damage die from 1d8 to 1d10 and gaining a +2 circumstance bonus to their damage roll for their next crossbow Strike, as long as it occurs before the end of their next turn.",
